Definition: plant having basal grasslike leaves and a narrow open cluster of starlike yellowish-orange flowers atop a leafless stalk
Example: southwestern United States; only species of Anthericum growing in North America
Synonyms: Anthericum_torreyi, liliaceous_plant, genus_Anthericum, m, plant, having, basal, grasslike, leaves, and, a, narrow, open, cluster, of, starlike, yellowish-orange, flowers, atop, leafless, stalk, southwestern, United, States, only, species, Anthericum, growing, in, North, America
Category: noun.plant
